    public class Chess110GUI
extends edu.kzoo.grid.gui.SteppedGridAppFrame
    Chess 110:
    A Chess110GUI object represents a window with control buttons and a display for a Chess 110 project. Most of the functionality is provided in the ActiveGridFrame superclass.
